  • Method Details

    • main

      public static void main(String[] args)
      The main method, the heart of our program that will do all operations This program objective is to apply the Split-and-Merge algorithm on an image
      Parameters:
      args - String[], in order args must contain: an homogeneity criteria (always between 0 and 1), a volumeMin value (the algorithm will not split a cube which is already under this volume but the splited cube obtained can be under this volume) a method value 0 for 1rst method anything else for the 2nd method, the path and name to the original image, the path and name of the new image
